Name: Forafric Global PLC Warrants
Description: Forafric Global PLC stands out as a premier agribusiness company dedicated to the production and distribution of high-quality food products across Africa. Committed to empowering communities through job creation and agricultural development, Forafric aligns its operational goals with broader socio-economic objectives.
